bjects, but with notable second order\ndifferences in the nature of turbulence, the enhancement of the star formation\nrate, and the number of massive clusters formed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 8 Sep 2017 18:21:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-11-01"}
